<br>
As a matter of law, it seems that there is no valid reason to deny anyone the right to marry another.  The function of a gay marriage in society's workforce is really no different than any traditional marriage.<br>
<br>
From a spiritual standpoint, if you believe in a particular written doctrine (that you deem &quot;inspired&quot;) and it condones any relations outside the bonds of marriage between a man and a woman, then gay marriage is wrong.<br>
<br>
Using a different example, I don't know of any religious doctrine that doesn't promote selfless acts for your fellow man as a first directive to spiritual progresssion.  In society, however, there is no law against being materialistic and selfish.  The more assets you have the more you're protected under law. <p><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/lorellelovecraft/ezsig2.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqfaces.com/cgi/files/engine/profile.php?personalID=472">The Lovecraft Family</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=300843">Lorelle</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~ <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=329619">Laurelle</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~ <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=646037">Lorele</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~ <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=650378">Loriele</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=baldrikthedorf>Baldrik the Dorf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.josh-leclair.com/uploads/docs/fairy_bounce08.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 516<br> <font color=#330000>(7/9/03 12:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=832.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Clearing some things up...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--